data.text:
Name Gojimir in modern Croatia

Gojimir is a male name, in Croatia principally Croatian, but also Serbian. It is one of the rare names in Croatia, with less than twenty namesakes living there.

Prevalence

Name Gojimir is present mainly in Dalmatia, and scarcely in North-West Croatia. Most of the persons named Gojimir live in the following cities and municipalities: Split (less than ten), Osijek (less than ten), Kutjevo (less than ten).

Mentions in sources

In the sources analysed in the project Acta Croatica so far, the name is mentioned few times, the first time 2007 in source Encyclopaedia of Croatian Surnames.
